Ntaoleng Patricia Peacock (amụrụ n'ụbọchị nke abụọ n'ọnwa Febụwarị n'afọ otu puku narị itoolu na iri asaa na asatọ ) bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị South Africa bụ onye otu National Assembly kemgbe Mee 2019
Peacock bụ onye otu African National Congress
Peacock bụ onye otu African National Congress
A họpụtara ya ka ọ nọchite anya pati ahụ na National Assembly of South Africa mgbe ntuli aka e mere na 8 Mee 2019. A ṅụrụ ya iyi dị ka onye omeiwu na 22 Mee 2019
N'abalị iri abụọ na asaa n'ọnwa Juun, ọ natara ọrụ kọmitii ya.
